cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with generative models for image composition, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of GANs for this purpose also makes it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the spatial layout and scaling of objects, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
